library(httr)
library(tidyverse)
ds = readRDS(file = "ds.rds")
for (id in setdiff(1:20000,ds$ID)){
  print(id)
  response = tryCatch(               
    expr = {            
      httr::GET(url = paste0("https://mnlthassets.rtfkt.com/",id))%>%
        content(., as="text")%>%
        rjson::fromJSON()
    },
    # Specifying error message
    error = function(e){         
      return("error")
    }
  )
  if( length(response)!=6){
    next
  }
  
  response$attributes%>%
    lapply(., function(x){
      data.frame(trait_type=x$trait_type,
                 value=x$value)%>%
        return()
    })%>%bind_rows()%>%
    spread(trait_type,value)%>%
    mutate(ID=id)%>%
    bind_rows(ds,.) -> ds
}
saveRDS(ds,file="ds.rds")
ds%>%
  group_by(DNA)%>%
  summarise(Freq=n())%>%
  mutate(Ratio=round(Freq/sum(Freq)*100,digits = 2)%>%paste0("%"))%>%
  arrange(desc(Freq))
